    <briefdescription>
<para>Implements the locally weighted regression method. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class inherits from the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1KernelRegressor" kindref="compound">KernelRegressor</ref> and implements locally weighted regression. It reuses the design matrices computed by the <ref refid="classkukadu_1_1GeneralFitter" kindref="compound">GeneralFitter</ref> class. </para>    </detaileddescription>
